Sentencas: Tubular-type solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) with interconnector has been successfully fabricated, with a maximum single cell power density of 0.9 W/cm(2), the highest value reported so far.
Titulo: FABRICATION OF HIGH-POWER DENSITY TUBULAR TYPE SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS

Sentencas: A self supporting La(Sr)MnOx tube was used for the cathode.
Titulo: FABRICATION OF HIGH-POWER DENSITY TUBULAR TYPE SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS

Sentencas: The La(Sr)CrOx interconnector was made using the laser ablation method.
Titulo: FABRICATION OF HIGH-POWER DENSITY TUBULAR TYPE SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS

Sentencas: The yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) electrolyte and Ru/ YSZ cermet anode were fabricated by the electrochemical vapor deposition (EVD) process.
Titulo: FABRICATION OF HIGH-POWER DENSITY TUBULAR TYPE SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS
